Coalition Soldier
Elite Coalition infantry wearing the iconic skull-faced Dead Boy armor.
This OCC is an alias for cs dead boy. See also help cs_dead_boy and occs.

Skill categories: Military, Physical, Pilot, Technical, W.P., Espionage.
Attribute requirements: IQ 8, PS 12, PE 12.
Starting equipment: Coalition Dead Boy body armor, C-20 laser pistol,
C-12 heavy assault rifle, four grenades, radio headset, and CS field kit.
